title: JulD Airdrop for the community
body:
First , I would like to thank the community to believe in this projects and shower their love to Julb and JulD. 

Now it's time , users should be rewarded. 
I am proposing on the behalf of whole community to schedule airdrop for users for using julswap platform.
Community may reward more to holders and liquidity providers.
